'''''Barry Harris Plays Tadd Dameron''''' is an album by pianist [[Barry Harris]] featuring compositions associated with [[Tadd Dameron]]. It was recorded in 1975 and released on the [[Xanadu Records|Xanadu]] label.<ref>[http://www.jazzlists.com/SJ_Label_Xanadu.htm Xanadu Records discography] accessed April 29, 2014</ref><ref>Fitzgerald, M. [http://www.jazzdiscography.com/Leaders/HarrisBarry-ldr.php Barry Harris discography], accessed April 29, 2014</ref>

