[[Allmusic]] awarded the album 4Â½ stars with its review by Scott Yanow stating, "The perfect player to interpret Tadd Dameron's music (of which he had full understanding), Harris performs eight of the influential composer's songs on this 1975 album".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S. [http://www.allmusic.com/album/barry-harris-plays-tadd-dameron-mw0000899911 Allmusic Review], accessed April 29, 2014</ref>

